// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1850 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c15ac927-16d7-5c2a-ad2c-ee019effd741

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
